  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to verify whether OPC-12759 ophthalmic solution is effective
      compared with placebo in dry eye patients. OPC-12759 ophthalmic suspension will be used as a
      reference drug.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
